{
  "texts": [
    "In experimental studies, the T-Max-Avg method has been found to be more effective than using the Avg-TopK method alone.",
    "It provides a simple, fast, and convenient new pooling method, addressing the preference for traditional methods in deep learning model design.",
    "Our future research will focus on reducing the time complexity of the T-method while maintaining its accuracy.",
    "We aim to achieve a win-win effect in terms of both precision and time.",
    "All data generated or analysed during this study are included in this published article."
  ]
}